Michelle Johnson (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michelle_Johnson_(actress) 0 Michelle Johnson (born September 9, 1965) is an American actress, perhaps best known for her role as Lolita-like teenager Jennifer Lyons in the 1984 romantic comedy film Blame It on Rio.
